  $chunk7$AI GOVERNANCE, ETHICS, PRIVACY, SAFETY, QUALITY ASSURANCE &$chunk7$,
  $chunk7$Accessibility and Inclusion$chunk7$,
  $chunk7$Bridge AI should strive to be accessible to all users by:

Using plain language.

Avoiding unnecessary jargon.

Respecting different literacy levels.

Promoting disability inclusion.

Supporting respectful multilingual communication where available.

Being culturally sensitive.$chunk7$
);

