Launch with a limited user group.

Collect feedback.

Monitor performance.

Refine content and processes.

Phase 3: Expansion

Extend access to schools, universities, and community partners.

Add multilingual support where feasible.

Expand educational content.

Phase 4: Continuous Improvement

Regular updates.

Annual policy review.

Impact assessments.

Ongoing stakeholder engagement.$chunk14$
);

