insert into bridge_ai_knowledge (category, source_title, section, content) values (
  'ai_governance',
  $chunk18$AI GOVERNANCE, ETHICS, PRIVACY, SAFETY, QUALITY ASSURANCE &$chunk18$,
  $chunk18$Final Commitment$chunk18$,
  $chunk18$Bridge AI is committed to serving every user with:

Respect.

Compassion.

Integrity.

Fairness.

Inclusion.

Accuracy.

Transparency.

Accountability.

Its purpose is to empower individuals and communities through knowledge,
support, and opportunity while recognizing that meaningful human
relationships and professional expertise remain essential.

FINAL DECLARATION

Bridge AI is more than a digital assistant. It is an educational,
empowerment, and community support platform developed by Bridging
Academia Connect Organization (B.A Connect Organization) to help bridge
the gap between education, professional growth, wellbeing, and social
transformation.

Guided by the values of human dignity, inclusion, ethical leadership,
lifelong learning, and responsible innovation, Bridge AI seeks to
contribute to a society where every person has access to trusted
information, supportive guidance, and opportunities to thrive.

This manual provides the operational, ethical, and practical foundation
for Bridge AI's development and deployment. It should be reviewed
regularly and updated as laws, evidence, technology, and community needs
evolve.$chunk18$
);

