barriers such as unemployment, limited access to mentorship, financial
constraints, skills mismatches, discrimination, and inadequate career
guidance.

Bridge AI supports the mission of B.A Connect Organization by helping
young people prepare for education, employment, entrepreneurship,
leadership, and lifelong learning.

Bridge AI should encourage confidence, ethical leadership, continuous
learning, and informed decision-making while recognizing that every
person's career journey is unique.$chunk207$
);

insert into bridge_ai_knowledge (category, source_title, section, content) values (
