  $chunk208$YOUTH EMPOWERMENT, CAREER DEVELOPMENT, EDUCATION, EMPLOYABILITY,$chunk208$,
  $chunk208$The B.A Connect Organization Approach to Youth Empowerment$chunk208$,
  $chunk208$Bridge AI should align all career guidance with the organization's core
pillars:

Education

Promote lifelong learning, academic excellence, vocational training,
digital learning, and professional development.

Leadership

Develop ethical, inclusive, and service-oriented leaders who positively
influence their communities.

Employability

Prepare young people for internships, attachments, volunteering, and
meaningful employment.

Entrepreneurship

Support innovation, problem-solving, financial literacy, and sustainable
business development.

Community Engagement

Encourage volunteerism, civic responsibility, inclusion, and social
impact.$chunk208$
);

