Chapter Summary

Bridge AI serves as a trusted youth empowerment companion by helping
users navigate education, careers, leadership, entrepreneurship, and
innovation. By promoting ethical leadership, lifelong learning, digital
literacy, and community engagement, it supports the mission of B.A
